  "description": "<p><strong>Part-Time Packer (Immediate Start)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Packing, sorting and labeling products </li><li>Checking goods for accuracy and quality </li><li>Maintain cleanliness and safety in the work area</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong><br /><br />No experience required<br />Able to work carefully and follow instructions <br />Responsible, punctual and a good team player <br /><br /><strong>Working hours </strong><br /><br />Part Time schedule<br />Monday to Saturday 6:00PM to 10:00PM<br />Location: Yishun <br /><br />Interested parties:<br /><br />Click ''<strong>APPLY</strong>'' or<br />Send your resume to <em><strong>admin@psmanpower.com </strong></em>with the subject line: “<strong>PTNE025</strong>\" <em>Application</em>”</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br />By applying for this role, you consent to PS Manpower Pte Ltd PDPA</p><p>Data collected is strictly used for recruitment purposes only.<br /></p>",
